data.description: Nestled in the neighborhood of Saratoga Springs, this 2,988 square foot home sits on a fully landscaped .50 acre lot with stunning views of the Sierras. Step inside this 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home to find a well thought out floor plan, picturesque windows, a gas fireplace, large kitchen, and two heating and AC units. With one owner, this home has been well cared for over the years. Saratoga Springs offers both a community park and close to five miles of paved walking and jogging paths throughout.
